{"tid":506979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會否考慮回購領展？林鄭：無講過會解決","createTime":"2017-12-22T17:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T08:53:40.000Z","uid":1886,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"82c2669743c7ec524c97eeabb32666ee7c7504ba","tid":506979,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"領展自2005年上市後不斷翻新及拆售旗下商場，使有關舖位大幅加租，小店買少見少，被各界批評漠視居民需要。特首林鄭月娥接受港台專訪時，重申政府不會回購領展，更形容回購是「無智慧、相當愚蠢」的做法。她又強調，由競選開始直到早前發表的《施政報告》，「都無作過任何承諾可以解決佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，面對領展問題，她甚至會覺得束手無策<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/22144211/image1513924817114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F22144211%2Fimage1513924817114.png&h=febcd275&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n然而，林鄭競選期間與上任後都曾多次向傳媒表示，領展是「三座大山」當中最難處理的一座。因為領展問題屬商業行為，政府沒有甚麼可以做，只可從制訂政策方面，例如重建市政街市等作出改善。按照林鄭的所言，她當日提出「三座大山」恐怕只是意指包括領展在內的三個問題「難以解決」，而非代表她有解決的決心或承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/238405/%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F238405%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%25EF%25BC%259F%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%2F&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=87a81d77\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/238405/%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A7%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%B1%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%EF%BC%9A/</a>"},{"pid":"48cfe87dc4d5f45ca8756b9bd970990b5dea4a26","tid":506979,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T17:58:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20171222/_2017122208263515055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20171222%2F_2017122208263515055.jpg&h=40ebca28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥接受電台專訪時，表明不會回購領展，會對公帑有很大損害。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1095050/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1095050%2F&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=0e0fe63f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1095050%2F&h=80498e66\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1095050/</a></div>"},{"pid":"558154938ef46c3c571737e8a653edf3dcb7b414","tid":506979,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1976524/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%9B%9E%E8%B3%BC%E9%A0%98%E5%B1%95%E3%80%80%E9%81%B8%E5%9D%80%E5%BB%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E8%A1%97%E5%B8%82%E4%B9%9F%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%A3%E5%BA%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1976524%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%25B1%2595%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%259D%2580%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25BA%25A6&d=Iy0naNJY9kzon15L2DFTHB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=1a071c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://topi